    "It does not provide enough additional recommendations, improvement prompts, training tips, or extra information to grow workers' knowledge.",
    "For accurate responses and a smooth experience, the customized data for the offline system needs to be well described and prepared before use.",
    "However, the online chatbot version directly connected to ChatGPT version 4 has the flexibility to assist workers beyond the provided data, assist users in formulating the correct queries, suggest several ways to improve the system, and respond to questions beyond the boxed-loaded data.Factories widely utilize HMIs and SCADA as monitoring interfaces between operators and machines.",
    "Under I5.0, their functions shift to more flexible, interactive, and intelligent tools that ease operators' monitoring tasks [51].",
    "Our GPT industrial chatbot qualifies as an I5.0 HMI by its ability to provide operators, through natural language queries/responses, the necessary information regarding their factory production and equipment statuses."
